or something, just wake me up.

417
00:32:48,512 --> 00:32:50,349
It's not nice
being scared alone.

418
00:32:54,557 --> 00:32:55,651
Thanks, Joe.

419
00:32:57,186 --> 00:32:58,390
You bet, doll.

420
00:34:05,857 --> 00:34:07,091
No!

421
00:34:07,193 --> 00:34:08,493
