431
00:34:26,517 --> 00:34:28,084
Dude, jump in!

432
00:34:29,048 --> 00:34:30,417
Get ready to move.

433
00:34:30,519 --> 00:34:32,253
- JOEL: Get the smoke.
- I gotta get the fuck
out of here!

434
00:34:36,056 --> 00:34:37,555
- Fuck!
- Slow down!

435
00:34:41,899 --> 00:34:44,633
