438
00:34:55,944 --> 00:34:57,245
(CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING)

439
00:34:58,111 --> 00:35:00,380
MAN 2: Fuck!
Fuck!

440
00:35:01,114 --> 00:35:02,282
