486
00:41:52,524 --> 00:41:53,793
JESSIE: Thanks.

487
00:41:57,695 --> 00:41:58,826
LEE: Don't forget to eat.

488
00:41:58,928 --> 00:42:00,129
JESSIE: Yeah, I'm starving.

489
00:42:03,966 --> 00:42:05,838
