just right?

494
00:42:17,316 --> 00:42:18,279
LEE: Hmm.

495
00:42:21,157 --> 00:42:22,486
Body temperature.

496
00:42:22,588 --> 00:42:24,120
- Smart.
- Thank you.

497
00:42:29,198 --> 00:42:34,229
So how about you tell me
