- Except, Colorado.

513
00:43:19,978 --> 00:43:22,816
Also pretending
this isn't happening.

514
00:43:23,613 --> 00:43:24,785
No shit.

515
00:43:28,851 --> 00:43:30,285
Hey, these are dry.

516
00:43:31,019 --> 00:43:32,322
You should check them out.

517
00:43:32,424 --> 00:43:34,058
Sure.

518
00:43:34,160 --> 00:43:36,324
